1000002700310@unknown@formal@none@1@S@To generate a string in the language, one begins with a string consisting of only a single ⌊/start symbol/⌋, and then successively applies the rules (any number of times, in any order) to rewrite this string.@@@@1@36@@oe@26-8-2013
